      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the same newspaper that our, you know, the little notice appeared that we got married.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The headline of that newspaper was, 'Hitler is Dead and the War is Almost Over.' And that was a very memorable day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I still have that newspaper too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we got married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, you know, we-- we lived in Bern then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother was free in Bern too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She wanted to be near me, so she took a job as a maid in a Swiss household.",
      "word_count": 18
